Quest._currentObjective: Find and return Mayor Lewis' purple shorts.
Quest._questDescription: Mayor Lewis has lost his purple "shorts". He's asking you to find and return them... Discreetly.

Quest._currentObjective: Reach level 25 in the Skull Cavern.
Quest._questDescription: You've been challenged to reach level 25 in the skull cavern. You've been promised a substantial reward if you're successful.
You found a note, barely legible, asking you to bring "may-pal serrup" to the "seecrit wuds".
It would be a nice gesture to introduce yourself around town. Some people might be anxious to meet the new farmer.
